 days). He joined The Beat to record their first single, "Tears of a Clown", <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref><ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%223%22])">3</ref> a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../031/159031.xml">
cover version</link> of the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../396/167396.xml">
